name: Kinton Ramen
description: Established in May 2012, KINTON RAMEN was one of the first Japanese ramen restaurants in Toronto. Led by Executive Chef Aki Urata and our team of professional ramen chefs, we strive to offer our guests an extraordinary dining experience every time. Using the freshest ingredients to make the best quality noodles and broths, we invite guests to taste our exceptional ramen bowls right down to the last drop.

description:
Nestled in the heart of downtown Kingston, on charming Brock St. you’ll find us! Our vibrant and upbeat atmosphere makes us a great spot for drinks with friends, a dinner date out, or a fun corporate lunch.

Enjoy our newly updated fall menu with the cozy flavours of autumn, paired with our well known staple menu items and thoughtfully crafted beverages.

Inside you’ll see our pizza masters at work alongside our talented bartenders working together to create a meaningful experience for each and every guest.
